ai_summary.en: Amidst a macro BTC Fear environment, whale sentiment presents a stark contrast between chains. On ETH, institutional money is largely neutral, observing with high volume and cautious stablecoin rebalancing rather than strong directional bets. Conversely, the more speculative SOL chain shows distinct bearish sentiment among whales, marked by very low activity and significant SOL outflow. This divergence suggests institutions are biding their time, while retail speculation has cooled, indicating continued market apprehension in the short term.
ai_summary.zh: 在宏观比特币恐惧情绪笼罩下，鲸鱼情绪在不同链上呈现鲜明对比。在以太坊上，机构资金基本持中性态度，交易量虽高但倾向于谨慎的稳定币再平衡，而非强烈的方向性押注。相比之下，更具投机性的SOL链则显示出鲸鱼明显的看跌情绪，其特点是极低的活跃度和显著的SOL流出。这种分歧表明机构正在观望，而散户投机情绪已显著降温，预示短期市场将持续担忧。
